snippet.title: AMBER HEARD TRAINS FOR AQUAMAN
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is playing Mera in both the Justice League movie and in the Aquaman film.

The 30-year-old actress posted a cool video showing off her training skills for the movie in addition to a pic with co-star Jason Momoa. 

"Another day at the office," Amber Heard posted on Instagram about the video and added about the photo: "Crush Monday."

Aquaman is currently filming in Australia.
